      },
      "date": "2013-06-16 13:28:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/90b91710-d688-11e2-949a-52540035b04c).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
