        "username": "maloo",
        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2013-07-04 10:11:25.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/7393bed2-e48f-11e2-a950-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "cc96388736a9b4e2e61ad58d5f376b477fdd8d3b",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 142
      },
      "date": "2013-07-04 23:19:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI ran tests to check that passed dentries are the same as being looked up: http://review.whamcloud.com/6869\n\nMany tests have failed. However, taking a closer look, it appears that vfs_rmdir and vfs_rename_dir call dentry_unhash before entering lustre, so dcache lookup should inevitably fail.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "87957192709c69f24fbe30bfe1b901e6e9bde357",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 3,
        "name": "Fan Yong",
        "email": "fan.yong@intel.com",
        "username": "nasf",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-07-08 12:54:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Andrew Perepechko\t\tJul 5 7:19 AM\n> I ran tests to check that passed dentries are the same as being looked up: http://review.whamcloud.com/6869\n> Many tests have failed. However, taking a closer look, it appears that vfs_rmdir and vfs_rename_dir call dentry_unhash before entering lustre, so dcache lookup should inevitably fail.\n\nPanda, you means the ELC does not work as we expected, but we did not notice the failures because of dentry_unhash() called before entering Lustre, right? If so, would you please to analysis more? Thanks!",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "fb7d2ed1b483ad68c5fd41df6fb8e66f58ed9cb5",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 142
      },
      "date": "2013-07-08 13:09:30.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nFan Yong, I mean that ELC did not work as expected because of dentry_unhash() called before rmdir and rename_dir and failing dcache lookup.\n\nBut this will be fixed with this patch.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
